  "body": "### Description\r\nSupport switching PoW algorithms (Keccak vs ethash) at a given block through a RPC method or a configuration.\r\n\r\nWe want to make it possible for folks to choose a new pow algorithm through RPC. When this pow method is selected, the client can be configured to change its pow algorithm at will, providing the block number is in the future.\r\n\r\n",
